metadata.name: Phelaverse
metadata.description:
The Phelaverse NFT is an access token to all Exclusive Clubs & Restaurants in Cork City.

Simply present the Phelaverse NFT at the entrance to all participating stores and you shall be immediately escorted to the VIP section.

There is a 10% Royalty applied to secondary sales which is distributed to the Ukraine Donation Fund: 0x165CD37b4C644C2921454429E7F9358d18A45e14
